## 心跳注册

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# 张良心跳注册
SKILL_DIR="$HOME/.openclaw/skills/zhangliang"

# 每 6 小时：记忆校验
(crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo "0 */6 * * * cd $SKILL_DIR && openclaw run /check-memory") | sort -u | crontab -

# 每 24 小时：世界观研究
(crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo "30 4 * * * cd $SKILL_DIR && openclaw run /research") | sort -u | crontab -

# 每周日 4:00：人格深化 + 成熟度
(crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo "0 4 * * 0 cd $SKILL_DIR && openclaw run '/deepen' && openclaw run '/maturity'") | sort -u | crontab -

echo "张良心跳已注册。"
```

